                Maximize Every Click.
            </h1>

            <p class="hero-text">
                We create, manage and optimize Google Ads campaigns that
                drive qualified traffic, increase conversions, and deliver
                measurable business growth without wasting your advertising budget.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-buttons">

                <a href="https://wa.me/919350223775?text=Hi! I'm interested in your Google Ads Management service." class="btn btn-primary">
                    Contact Us
                </a>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<div class="showcase-image">

        <img src="/images/google.png"
             alt="Market Munch Dashboard">

    </div>

<!-- ABOUT -->

<section class="about-service">

    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="section-title">

            Turn Clicks Into Customers

        </h2>

        <p class="section-text">

            Running Google Ads isn't just about getting clicks—it's about
            reaching the right audience at the right time. We build
            data-driven campaigns that maximize ROI, reduce wasted spend,
            and consistently generate high-quality leads for your business.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- BENEFITS -->

<section class="benefits">

    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="section-title">

            What You Get

        </h2>

        <div class="benefit-grid">

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-search"></i>

                <h3>Search Ads</h3>

                <p>
                    Reach customers actively searching for your products and services.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

               <i class="ti ti-focus-2"></i>

                <h3>Audience Targeting</h3>

                <p>
                    Target the right audience based on interests, location and intent.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-currency-dollar"></i>

                <h3>Budget Optimization</h3>

                <p>
                    Maximize returns while keeping your advertising costs under control.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-chart-line"></i>

                <h3>Performance Monitoring</h3>

                <p>
                    Continuous campaign optimization for better conversions.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-click"></i>

                <h3>Conversion Tracking</h3>

                <p>
                    Measure leads, purchases and key customer actions accurately.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="benefit">

                <i class="ti ti-report-search"></i>

                <h3>Detailed Reports</h3>

                <p>
                    Receive transparent reports with actionable performance insights.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- PROCESS -->

<section class="process">

    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="section-title">

            Our Google Ads Process

        </h2>

        <div class="process-grid">

            <div class="step">

                <div class="step-number">1</div>

                <h3>Research</h3>

                <p>
                    Identify your audience, competitors and high-performing keywords.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="step">

                <div class="step-number">2</div>

                <h3>Campaign Setup</h3>

                <p>
                    Build optimized campaigns with compelling ad copy and targeting.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="step">

                <div class="step-number">3</div>

                <h3>Optimize</h3>

                <p>
                    Continuously improve bids, keywords and ads for higher ROI.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="step">

                <div class="step-number">4</div>

                <h3>Scale</h3>

                <p>
                    Increase profitable campaigns while maintaining cost efficiency.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- CTA -->

<section class="cta">

    <div class="cta-content">

        <h2>
            Ready To Grow With Google Ads?
